    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. To make it even more impactful for the scene, can you expand on that? Maybe add some specific details about the \"savagery\" he's seeing—like their living conditions or their lack of \"proper\" religion and technology—to really drive home why he feels it's his moral duty to step in and civilize them. Make it feel like he truly believes he's doing them a favor.",
